              <p class="body-m">(B)&nbsp; <strong class="tracking-header">Education Version.</strong> &nbsp;If we designate the Services and Software to be for use by educational users (“<strong class="tracking-header">Educational Version</strong>”), then you may use the Educational Version only if you meet the eligibility requirements stated at&nbsp;<a href="/go/primary-secondary-institution-eligibility-guidelines/" data-has-dnt="true" daa-ll="https www adobe com -1--Educational Version">https://www.adobe.com/go/primary-secondary-institution-eligibility-guidelines</a>. You may install and use the Educational Version only in the country where you are qualified as an educational user. If you reside in the EEA, then the word “country” in the prior sentence means the EEA.</p>
